Arellano University It is located in the University Belt sub - district of Manila . And its address is 2600 Legarda St , Sampaloc Area , Manila City . Arellano University also known as A.U . The university was named for former Chief Justice of the Philippines , Cayetano Arellano . Arellano University has seven branches in Metro Manila . Atty. Roland A. Niedo - Sr . Prof. Mario F. Sales - Asst . Prof. Zenaida M. Lobrergat - Asst . Prof. Elena T. Rodriguez - Asst . This article does not cite any references or sources . Please help ] improve this article ] by adding citations to reliable sources . Unverifiable material may be challenged and removed . This Asian university , college or other education institution article is a stub . 